# Public Portfolio repo policy:
# Track ONLY README.md + LICENSE on the public remote.
# Everything else is excluded so nothing leaks via `git add` mistakes.

# Default-deny everything
*

# Allow only what is meant to be public
!.gitignore
!README.md
!LICENSE

# Never publish source, secrets, internal docs, build output, assets, deps
node_modules/
.next/
out/
build/
.env
.env.*
.DS_Store
*.log
docs/
memory/
plans/
.claude/
